Self Review 1 — Responsibility and Approval
1. Activation and rollback authority initially too close -> separated Product/Operations joint Go, Operations rollback judgment, Release execution.
2. Role labels could hide missing people -> named assignee register uses UNASSIGNED / OPEN_BLOCKER.
3. Approval cancellation/expiry absent -> 30-day and source/incident reversal rules added.
Result: 3 findings, 3 remediated.
